{"tid":2211519,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"李梓敬的造謠手法 - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-09-21T07:37:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T08:11:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9d6707965fbd7ada687b86a3c52e8bb3b9317aac","tid":2211519,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T07:37:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200921/L76FFCFXZRD53LEOFCYWARI5EE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200921%2FL76FFCFXZRD53LEOFCYWARI5EE%2F&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZolMsCyrUT%2FuZDySwcdaP%2B5k%3D&h=7000e8a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200921%2FL76FFCFXZRD53LEOFCYWARI5EE%2F&h=85e73d3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200921/L76FFCFXZRD53LEOFCYWARI5EE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n李梓敬的造謠手法 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/n3TXcaFAtMgcxNTp5mlyHmbpC6U=/850x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/X34W3QBTZZESPIVX7L4TSVZ5J4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fn3TXcaFAtMgcxNTp5mlyHmbpC6U%3D%2F850x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FX34W3QBTZZESPIVX7L4TSVZ5J4.jpg&h=5d276024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李梓敬fb截圖<br />\n<br />\n傳媒人柳俊江與男子動武，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n我皺着眉頭，掃視他的垃圾專頁，多是惡意散播的謠言、斷章取義的新聞，但幾乎每帖都有二至六千「腦殘藍」讚好。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n九月十二日，。。。。。。。。。。問題是：為什麼李梓敬不貼出新聞原文鏈結呢？<br />\n<br />\n答案很簡單：看了原文，就沒那麼容易被西門梓煽惑了。<br />\n<br />\n我按圖索驥查閱《星島網》內文，發現首段已說：。。。。。。。。。，跟三月底官媒抹黑意大利的方法，一模一樣（詳見拙文〈向意大利的傷口撒鹽〉）。<br />\n<br />\n九月十三日，李梓敬發帖說：「12瞞徒淨係偷渡被捕，家屬都出晒嚟。點解831死咗幾千人，一個家屬都冇出嚟？」說「831死咗幾千人」即使不是造謠，也是卑鄙無恥的「打稻草人」詭辯&mdash;&mdash;根本沒有人（除非西門梓也算是所謂「人」）說831死幾千人，這樣說是刻意扭曲對方觀點，意圖削弱公眾質疑831的論據。試想：假設831死了幾個平凡人，被歸類「失蹤人口」，家屬如何得知？憑什麼開記招？<br />\n<br />\n最噁心的，是李梓敬專頁的簡介：。。。。。。"},{"pid":"8ff34212480127e2b8cc0cab59314868fe255a97","tid":2211519,"uid":304431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T07:39:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95f49820e3341409ced6f83104d688154558089c","tid":2211519,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:08:29.000Z","msg":"我想嘔呀。......."},{"pid":"ed572527b531f511ae21c773c6a44631514f3ff5","tid":2211519,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:11:06.000Z","msg":"呢隻曱甴好廢<br />\n<br />\n唔夠人駁正係識請人24小時block人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}